headline: Southwest, American Earnings Will Test the Airline-Stock Rally
summary: Airline stocks have soared this earnings season.  Results from  Southwest Airlines  and  American Airlines  will be a big test of the sector’s burgeoning comeback.  Earnings from  Delta Air Lines  and  United Airlines  earlier this month have restored some much-needed confidence in the industry.
